QuestData.Title: Enormous Eel Egg
QuestData.Description: <This appears to be an egg from one of the devious great-eels that float up above the canyon. You wonder whether or not Humphrey might be interested in something like this.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Deliver the Enormous Eel Egg to Humphrey Digsong at the bottom of Underlight Canyon in Vashj'ir.
QuestData.RewardText: Whaaa... an egg? An EEL egg?$b$b<Even upside-down, you can see the gears in Humphrey's head turning.>$b$bWe can definitely do something with this! Get ready kid, 'cause it's time for some good ol'-fashioned Digsong revenge!
